to a nation

05:14.214 --> 05:18.718 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on edge after days of bloodshed,
protest and
racial tension:

05:18.752 --> 05:21.788 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States:
It's as if the deepest fault
lines of our

05:21.821 --> 05:27.127 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
