wonder if the
divides of race in America can
ever be bridged.

05:46.046 --> 05:55.322 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I understand how Americans are
feeling. But,
Dallas, I'm here to say, we must
reject such

05:55.355 --> 06:01.695 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
