07:04.624 --> 07:09.562 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: When all this
takes place more
than 50 years after the passage
of the Civil

07:09.596 --> 07:18.138 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
