07:21.308 --> 07:28.581 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: We also know that
so much of
the tensions between police
departments and

07:28.615 --> 07:35.588 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
