08:08.121 --> 08:10.490 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GEORGE W. BUSH, Former President
of the United
States: Most of us imagine, if
the moment

08:10.523 --> 08:18.998 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
