dentist and
a doctor.

44:31.035 --> 44:39.944 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There was a tiny baby, well,
1-year-old, naked,
hit in the left chest. The
doctors just said,

44:39.977 --> 44:44.315 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
we can't do anything. And we had
to watch
the baby's little tummy,
desperate for breath,

44:44.348 --> 44:45.850 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
die.

44:45.883 --> 44:49.120 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Hours later,
the building
where she was working was hit.

44:49.153 --> 44:53.224 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Cathleen Colvin believes the
Assad regime
intentionally targeted her
sister, and she

44:53.257 --> 44:57.495 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
