conflict

47:14.465 --> 47:16.200 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
zones.

47:16.233 --> 47:22.139 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CATHLEEN COLVIN: As Marie said,
