escape the spotlight and try to
live a normal

51:27.284 --> 51:28.953 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
life.

51:28.986 --> 51:31.288 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SUSAN FORD BALES, Daughter of
